{"surah":{"number":65,"name":"الطلاق","englishName":"At-Talaq","englishTranslation":"The Divorce","ayahCount":12},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:26.831Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"O Prophet, when you [Muslims] divorce women, divorce them for [the commencement of] their waiting period and keep count of the waiting period, and fear Allah, your Lord. Do not turn them out of their [husbands'] houses, nor should they [themselves] leave [during that period] unless they are committing a clear immorality. And those are the limits [set by] Allah. And whoever transgresses the limits of Allah has certainly wronged himself. You know not; perhaps Allah will bring about after that a [different] matter.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","english":"O","translit":"yāayyuhā","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّبِىُّ","english":"Prophet","translit":"l-nabiyu","root":"نبأ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"طَلَّقْتُمُ","english":"you divorce","translit":"ṭallaqtumu","root":"طلق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلنِّسَآءَ","english":"[the] women","translit":"l-nisāa","root":"نسو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَطَلِّقُوهُنَّ","english":"then divorce them","translit":"faṭalliqūhunna","root":"طلق"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لِعِدَّتِهِنَّ","english":"for their waiting period","translit":"liʿiddatihinna","root":"عدد"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَأَحْصُوا۟","english":"and keep count","translit":"wa-aḥṣū","root":"حصي"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْعِدَّةَ ۖ","english":"(of) the waiting period","translit":"l-ʿidata","root":"عدد"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَٱتَّقُوا۟","english":"and fear","translit":"wa-ittaqū","root":"وقي","audio":"wbw/065_001_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_001_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"رَبَّكُمْ ۖ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbakum","root":"ربب","audio":"wbw/065_001_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"لَا","english":"(Do) not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_015.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"تُخْرِجُوهُنَّ","english":"expel them","translit":"tukh'rijūhunna","root":"خرج","audio":"wbw/065_001_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"مِنۢ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"بُيُوتِهِنَّ","english":"their houses","translit":"buyūtihinna","root":"بيت","audio":"wbw/065_001_018.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_019.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"يَخْرُجْنَ","english":"they should leave","translit":"yakhruj'na","root":"خرج","audio":"wbw/065_001_020.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_021.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_022.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"يَأْتِينَ","english":"they commit","translit":"yatīna","root":"أتي","audio":"wbw/065_001_023.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"بِفَـٰحِشَةٍۢ","english":"an immorality","translit":"bifāḥishatin","root":"فحش","audio":"wbw/065_001_024.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"مُّبَيِّنَةٍۢ ۚ","english":"clear","translit":"mubayyinatin","root":"بين","audio":"wbw/065_001_025.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"وَتِلْكَ","english":"And these","translit":"watil'ka","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_027.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"حُدُودُ","english":"(are the) limits","translit":"ḥudūdu","root":"حدد","audio":"wbw/065_001_028.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ ۚ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_001_029.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_031.mp3"},{"position":28,"arabic":"يَتَعَدَّ","english":"transgresses","translit":"yataʿadda","root":"عدو","audio":"wbw/065_001_032.mp3"},{"position":29,"arabic":"حُدُودَ","english":"(the) limits","translit":"ḥudūda","root":"حدد","audio":"wbw/065_001_033.mp3"},{"position":30,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_001_034.mp3"},{"position":31,"arabic":"فَقَدْ","english":"then certainly","translit":"faqad","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_035.mp3"},{"position":32,"arabic":"ظَلَمَ","english":"he has wronged","translit":"ẓalama","root":"ظلم","audio":"wbw/065_001_036.mp3"},{"position":33,"arabic":"نَفْسَهُۥ ۚ","english":"himself","translit":"nafsahu","root":"نفس","audio":"wbw/065_001_037.mp3"},{"position":34,"arabic":"لَا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_039.mp3"},{"position":35,"arabic":"تَدْرِى","english":"you know","translit":"tadrī","root":"دري","audio":"wbw/065_001_040.mp3"},{"position":36,"arabic":"لَعَلَّ","english":"Perhaps","translit":"laʿalla","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_041.mp3"},{"position":37,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_001_042.mp3"},{"position":38,"arabic":"يُحْدِثُ","english":"will bring about","translit":"yuḥ'dithu","root":"حدث","audio":"wbw/065_001_043.mp3"},{"position":39,"arabic":"بَعْدَ","english":"after","translit":"baʿda","root":"بعد","audio":"wbw/065_001_044.mp3"},{"position":40,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"that","translit":"dhālika","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_001_045.mp3"},{"position":41,"arabic":"أَمْرًۭا","english":"a matter","translit":"amran","root":"أمر","audio":"wbw/065_001_046.mp3"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And when they have [nearly] fulfilled their term, either retain them according to acceptable terms or part with them according to acceptable terms. And bring to witness two just men from among you and establish the testimony for [the acceptance of] Allah. That is instructed to whoever should believe in Allah and the Last day. And whoever fears Allah - He will make for him a way out","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","english":"Then when","translit":"fa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَلَغْنَ","english":"they have reached","translit":"balaghna","root":"بلغ"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَجَلَهُنَّ","english":"their term","translit":"ajalahunna","root":"أجل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَأَمْسِكُوهُنَّ","english":"then retain them","translit":"fa-amsikūhunna","root":"مسك"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِمَعْرُوفٍ","english":"with kindness","translit":"bimaʿrūfin","root":"عرف"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"فَارِقُوهُنَّ","english":"part with them","translit":"fāriqūhunna","root":"فرق"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِمَعْرُوفٍۢ","english":"with kindness","translit":"bimaʿrūfin","root":"عرف"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَأَشْهِدُوا۟","english":"And take witness","translit":"wa-ashhidū","root":"شهد"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ذَوَىْ","english":"two men","translit":"dhaway","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"عَدْلٍۢ","english":"just","translit":"ʿadlin","root":"عدل"},{"position":12,"arabic":"مِّنكُمْ","english":"among you","translit":"minkum","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"وَأَقِيمُوا۟","english":"and establish","translit":"wa-aqīmū","root":"قوم"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱلشَّهَـٰدَةَ","english":"the testimony","translit":"l-shahādata","root":"شهد"},{"position":15,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ ۚ","english":"for Allah","translit":"lillahi","root":"أله"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكُمْ","english":"That","translit":"dhālikum","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_002_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"يُوعَظُ","english":"is instructed","translit":"yūʿaẓu","root":"وعظ","audio":"wbw/065_002_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"with it","translit":"bihi","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_002_019.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"مَن","english":"whoever","translit":"man","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_002_020.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"[is]","translit":"kāna","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/065_002_021.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُ","english":"believes","translit":"yu'minu","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/065_002_022.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","english":"in Allah","translit":"bil-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_002_023.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"وَٱلْيَوْمِ","english":"and the Day","translit":"wal-yawmi","root":"يوم","audio":"wbw/065_002_024.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرِ ۚ","english":"the Last","translit":"l-ākhiri","root":"أخر","audio":"wbw/065_002_025.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_002_027.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"يَتَّقِ","english":"fears","translit":"yattaqi","root":"وقي","audio":"wbw/065_002_028.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_002_029.mp3"},{"position":28,"arabic":"يَجْعَل","english":"He will make","translit":"yajʿal","root":"جعل","audio":"wbw/065_002_030.mp3"},{"position":29,"arabic":"لَّهُۥ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_002_031.mp3"},{"position":30,"arabic":"مَخْرَجًۭا","english":"a way out","translit":"makhrajan","root":"خرج","audio":"wbw/065_002_032.mp3"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And will provide for him from where he does not expect. And whoever relies upon Allah - then He is sufficient for him. Indeed, Allah will accomplish His purpose. Allah has already set for everything a [decreed] extent.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَرْزُقْهُ","english":"And He will provide for him","translit":"wayarzuq'hu","root":"رزق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَيْثُ","english":"where","translit":"ḥaythu","root":"حيث"},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَحْتَسِبُ ۚ","english":"he thinks","translit":"yaḥtasibu","root":"حسب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_003_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَتَوَكَّلْ","english":"puts his trust","translit":"yatawakkal","root":"وكل","audio":"wbw/065_003_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"upon","translit":"ʿalā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_003_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_003_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَهُوَ","english":"then He","translit":"fahuwa","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_003_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"حَسْبُهُۥٓ ۚ","english":"(is) sufficient for him","translit":"ḥasbuhu","root":"حسب","audio":"wbw/065_003_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_003_014.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_003_015.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"بَـٰلِغُ","english":"(will) accomplish","translit":"bālighu","root":"بلغ","audio":"wbw/065_003_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"أَمْرِهِۦ ۚ","english":"His purpose","translit":"amrihi","root":"أمر","audio":"wbw/065_003_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"Indeed","translit":"qad","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_003_019.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"جَعَلَ","english":"has set","translit":"jaʿala","root":"جعل","audio":"wbw/065_003_020.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_003_021.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"لِكُلِّ","english":"for every","translit":"likulli","root":"كلل","audio":"wbw/065_003_022.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ","audio":"wbw/065_003_023.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"قَدْرًۭا","english":"a measure","translit":"qadran","root":"قدر","audio":"wbw/065_003_024.mp3"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And those who no longer expect menstruation among your women - if you doubt, then their period is three months, and [also for] those who have not menstruated. And for those who are pregnant, their term is until they give birth. And whoever fears Allah - He will make for him of his matter ease.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّـٰٓـِٔى","english":"And those who","translit":"wa-allāī","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَئِسْنَ","english":"have despaired","translit":"ya-is'na","root":"يأس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَحِيضِ","english":"the menstruation","translit":"l-maḥīḍi","root":"حيض"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","english":"among","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"نِّسَآئِكُمْ","english":"your women","translit":"nisāikum","root":"نسو"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِنِ","english":"if","translit":"ini","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱرْتَبْتُمْ","english":"you doubt","translit":"ir'tabtum","root":"ريب"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فَعِدَّتُهُنَّ","english":"then their waiting period","translit":"faʿiddatuhunna","root":"عدد"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ثَلَـٰثَةُ","english":"(is) three","translit":"thalāthatu","root":"ثلث"},{"position":11,"arabic":"أَشْهُرٍۢ","english":"months","translit":"ashhurin","root":"شهر"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَٱلَّـٰٓـِٔى","english":"and the ones who","translit":"wa-allāī","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"لَمْ","english":"not","translit":"lam","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"يَحِضْنَ ۚ","english":"[they] menstruated","translit":"yaḥiḍ'na","root":"حيض"},{"position":15,"arabic":"وَأُو۟لَـٰتُ","english":"And those who (are)","translit":"wa-ulātu","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_004_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ٱلْأَحْمَالِ","english":"pregnant","translit":"l-aḥmāli","root":"حمل","audio":"wbw/065_004_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"أَجَلُهُنَّ","english":"their term","translit":"ajaluhunna","root":"أجل","audio":"wbw/065_004_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"أَن","english":"until","translit":"an","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_004_019.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"يَضَعْنَ","english":"they deliver","translit":"yaḍaʿna","root":"وضع","audio":"wbw/065_004_020.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"حَمْلَهُنَّ ۚ","english":"their burdens","translit":"ḥamlahunna","root":"حمل","audio":"wbw/065_004_021.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_004_023.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"يَتَّقِ","english":"fears","translit":"yattaqi","root":"وقي","audio":"wbw/065_004_024.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_004_025.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"يَجْعَل","english":"He will make","translit":"yajʿal","root":"جعل","audio":"wbw/065_004_026.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"لَّهُۥ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_004_027.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"of","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_004_028.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"أَمْرِهِۦ","english":"his affair","translit":"amrihi","root":"أمر","audio":"wbw/065_004_029.mp3"},{"position":28,"arabic":"يُسْرًۭا","english":"ease","translit":"yus'ran","root":"يسر","audio":"wbw/065_004_030.mp3"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"That is the command of Allah, which He has sent down to you; and whoever fears Allah - He will remove for him his misdeeds and make great for him his reward.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"That","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَمْرُ","english":"(is the) Command","translit":"amru","root":"أمر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَنزَلَهُۥٓ","english":"which He has sent down","translit":"anzalahu","root":"نزل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِلَيْكُمْ ۚ","english":"to you","translit":"ilaykum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"and whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_005_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَتَّقِ","english":"fears","translit":"yattaqi","root":"وقي","audio":"wbw/065_005_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_005_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يُكَفِّرْ","english":"He will remove","translit":"yukaffir","root":"كفر","audio":"wbw/065_005_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"عَنْهُ","english":"from him","translit":"ʿanhu","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_005_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"سَيِّـَٔاتِهِۦ","english":"his evil deeds","translit":"sayyiātihi","root":"سوأ","audio":"wbw/065_005_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَيُعْظِمْ","english":"and make great","translit":"wayuʿ'ẓim","root":"عظم","audio":"wbw/065_005_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"لَهُۥٓ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_005_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"أَجْرًا","english":"(his) reward","translit":"ajran","root":"أجر","audio":"wbw/065_005_015.mp3"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"Lodge them [in a section] of where you dwell out of your means and do not harm them in order to oppress them. And if they should be pregnant, then spend on them until they give birth. And if they breastfeed for you, then give them their payment and confer among yourselves in the acceptable way; but if you are in discord, then there may breastfeed for the father another woman.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَسْكِنُوهُنَّ","english":"Lodge them","translit":"askinūhunna","root":"سكن"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَيْثُ","english":"where","translit":"ḥaythu","root":"حيث"},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَكَنتُم","english":"you dwell","translit":"sakantum","root":"سكن"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"(out) of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"وُجْدِكُمْ","english":"your means","translit":"wuj'dikum","root":"وجد"},{"position":7,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and (do) not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"تُضَآرُّوهُنَّ","english":"harm them","translit":"tuḍārrūhunna","root":"ضرر"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لِتُضَيِّقُوا۟","english":"to distress","translit":"lituḍayyiqū","root":"ضيق"},{"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِنَّ ۚ","english":"[on] them","translit":"ʿalayhinna","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"وَإِن","english":"And if","translit":"wa-in","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"كُنَّ","english":"they are","translit":"kunna","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/065_006_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰتِ","english":"those (who are)","translit":"ulāti","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"حَمْلٍۢ","english":"pregnant","translit":"ḥamlin","root":"حمل","audio":"wbw/065_006_015.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"فَأَنفِقُوا۟","english":"then spend","translit":"fa-anfiqū","root":"نفق","audio":"wbw/065_006_016.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِنَّ","english":"on them","translit":"ʿalayhinna","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"حَتَّىٰ","english":"until","translit":"ḥattā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"يَضَعْنَ","english":"they deliver","translit":"yaḍaʿna","root":"وضع","audio":"wbw/065_006_019.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"حَمْلَهُنَّ ۚ","english":"their burden","translit":"ḥamlahunna","root":"حمل","audio":"wbw/065_006_020.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"فَإِنْ","english":"Then if","translit":"fa-in","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_022.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"أَرْضَعْنَ","english":"they suckle","translit":"arḍaʿna","root":"رضع","audio":"wbw/065_006_023.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_024.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"فَـَٔاتُوهُنَّ","english":"then give them","translit":"faātūhunna","root":"أتي","audio":"wbw/065_006_025.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"أُجُورَهُنَّ ۖ","english":"their payment","translit":"ujūrahunna","root":"أجر","audio":"wbw/065_006_026.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"وَأْتَمِرُوا۟","english":"and consult","translit":"watamirū","root":"أمر","audio":"wbw/065_006_028.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"بَيْنَكُم","english":"among yourselves","translit":"baynakum","root":"بين","audio":"wbw/065_006_029.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"بِمَعْرُوفٍۢ ۖ","english":"with kindness","translit":"bimaʿrūfin","root":"عرف","audio":"wbw/065_006_030.mp3"},{"position":28,"arabic":"وَإِن","english":"but if","translit":"wa-in","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_032.mp3"},{"position":29,"arabic":"تَعَاسَرْتُمْ","english":"you disagree","translit":"taʿāsartum","root":"عسر","audio":"wbw/065_006_033.mp3"},{"position":30,"arabic":"فَسَتُرْضِعُ","english":"then may suckle","translit":"fasatur'ḍiʿu","root":"رضع","audio":"wbw/065_006_034.mp3"},{"position":31,"arabic":"لَهُۥٓ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_006_035.mp3"},{"position":32,"arabic":"أُخْرَىٰ","english":"another (women)","translit":"ukh'rā","root":"أخر","audio":"wbw/065_006_036.mp3"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"Let a man of wealth spend from his wealth, and he whose provision is restricted - let him spend from what Allah has given him. Allah does not charge a soul except [according to] what He has given it. Allah will bring about, after hardship, ease.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِيُنفِقْ","english":"Let spend","translit":"liyunfiq","root":"نفق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذُو","english":"owner","translit":"dhū","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"سَعَةٍۢ","english":"(of) ample means","translit":"saʿatin","root":"وسع"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"سَعَتِهِۦ ۖ","english":"his ample means","translit":"saʿatihi","root":"وسع"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"and (he) who","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_007_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"قُدِرَ","english":"is restricted","translit":"qudira","root":"قدر","audio":"wbw/065_007_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"on him","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_007_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"رِزْقُهُۥ","english":"his provision","translit":"riz'quhu","root":"رزق","audio":"wbw/065_007_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"فَلْيُنفِقْ","english":"let him spend","translit":"falyunfiq","root":"نفق","audio":"wbw/065_007_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"مِمَّآ","english":"from what","translit":"mimmā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_007_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"ءَاتَىٰهُ","english":"he has been given","translit":"ātāhu","root":"أتي","audio":"wbw/065_007_013.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","english":"(by) Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_007_014.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"لَا","english":"Does not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_007_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"يُكَلِّفُ","english":"burden","translit":"yukallifu","root":"كلف","audio":"wbw/065_007_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_007_018.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"نَفْسًا","english":"any soul","translit":"nafsan","root":"نفس","audio":"wbw/065_007_019.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"except","translit":"illā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_007_020.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"(with) what","translit":"mā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_007_021.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"ءَاتَىٰهَا ۚ","english":"He has given it","translit":"ātāhā","root":"أتي","audio":"wbw/065_007_022.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"سَيَجْعَلُ","english":"Will bring about","translit":"sayajʿalu","root":"جعل","audio":"wbw/065_007_024.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_007_025.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"بَعْدَ","english":"after","translit":"baʿda","root":"بعد","audio":"wbw/065_007_026.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"عُسْرٍۢ","english":"hardship","translit":"ʿus'rin","root":"عسر","audio":"wbw/065_007_027.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"يُسْرًۭا","english":"ease","translit":"yus'ran","root":"يسر","audio":"wbw/065_007_028.mp3"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"And how many a city was insolent toward the command of its Lord and His messengers, so We took it to severe account and punished it with a terrible punishment.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَكَأَيِّن","english":"And how many","translit":"waka-ayyin","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"of","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَرْيَةٍ","english":"a town","translit":"qaryatin","root":"قري"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَتَتْ","english":"rebelled","translit":"ʿatat","root":"عتو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَنْ","english":"against","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَمْرِ","english":"(the) Command","translit":"amri","root":"أمر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"رَبِّهَا","english":"(of) its Lord","translit":"rabbihā","root":"ربب"},{"position":8,"arabic":"وَرُسُلِهِۦ","english":"and His Messengers","translit":"warusulihi","root":"رسل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"فَحَاسَبْنَـٰهَا","english":"so We took it to account","translit":"faḥāsabnāhā","root":"حسب"},{"position":10,"arabic":"حِسَابًۭا","english":"an account","translit":"ḥisāban","root":"حسب"},{"position":11,"arabic":"شَدِيدًۭا","english":"severe","translit":"shadīdan","root":"شدد"},{"position":12,"arabic":"وَعَذَّبْنَـٰهَا","english":"and We punished it","translit":"waʿadhabnāhā","root":"عذب"},{"position":13,"arabic":"عَذَابًۭا","english":"a punishment","translit":"ʿadhāban","root":"عذب"},{"position":14,"arabic":"نُّكْرًۭا","english":"terrible","translit":"nuk'ran","root":"نكر"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And it tasted the bad consequence of its affair, and the outcome of its affair was loss.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَذَاقَتْ","english":"So it tasted","translit":"fadhāqat","root":"ذوق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَبَالَ","english":"(the bad) consequence","translit":"wabāla","root":"وبل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَمْرِهَا","english":"(of) its affair","translit":"amrihā","root":"أمر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَكَانَ","english":"and was","translit":"wakāna","root":"كون"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَـٰقِبَةُ","english":"(the) end","translit":"ʿāqibatu","root":"عقب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَمْرِهَا","english":"(of) its affair","translit":"amrihā","root":"أمر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"خُسْرًا","english":"loss","translit":"khus'ran","root":"خسر"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"Allah has prepared for them a severe punishment; so fear Allah, O you of understanding who have believed. Allah has sent down to you the Qur'an.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَعَدَّ","english":"Has prepared","translit":"aʿadda","root":"عدد"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"for them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَذَابًۭا","english":"a punishment","translit":"ʿadhāban","root":"عذب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"شَدِيدًۭا ۖ","english":"severe","translit":"shadīdan","root":"شدد"},{"position":6,"arabic":"فَٱتَّقُوا۟","english":"So fear","translit":"fa-ittaqū","root":"وقي","audio":"wbw/065_010_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_010_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأُو۟لِى","english":"O men","translit":"yāulī","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_010_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَلْبَـٰبِ","english":"(of) understanding","translit":"l-albābi","root":"لبب","audio":"wbw/065_010_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_010_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟ ۚ","english":"have believed","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/065_010_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"Indeed","translit":"qad","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_010_014.mp3"},{"position":13,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","english":"Has sent down","translit":"anzala","root":"نزل","audio":"wbw/065_010_015.mp3"},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_010_016.mp3"},{"position":15,"arabic":"إِلَيْكُمْ","english":"to you","translit":"ilaykum","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_010_017.mp3"},{"position":16,"arabic":"ذِكْرًۭا","english":"a Message","translit":"dhik'ran","root":"ذكر","audio":"wbw/065_010_018.mp3"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"[He sent] a Messenger [Muhammad] reciting to you the distinct verses of Allah that He may bring out those who believe and do righteous deeds from darknesses into the light. And whoever believes in Allah and does righteousness - He will admit him into gardens beneath which rivers flow to abide therein forever. Allah will have perfected for him a provision.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"رَّسُولًۭا","english":"A Messenger","translit":"rasūlan","root":"رسل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَتْلُوا۟","english":"reciting","translit":"yatlū","root":"تلو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","english":"to you","translit":"ʿalaykum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتِ","english":"(the) Verses","translit":"āyāti","root":"أيي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","english":"(of) Allah","translit":"l-lahi","root":"أله"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مُبَيِّنَـٰتٍۢ","english":"clear","translit":"mubayyinātin","root":"بين"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لِّيُخْرِجَ","english":"that he may bring out","translit":"liyukh'rija","root":"خرج"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","english":"believe","translit":"āmanū","root":"أمن"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَعَمِلُوا۟","english":"and do","translit":"waʿamilū","root":"عمل"},{"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ","english":"righteous deeds","translit":"l-ṣāliḥāti","root":"صلح"},{"position":12,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"from","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلظُّلُمَـٰتِ","english":"the darkness[es]","translit":"l-ẓulumāti","root":"ظلم"},{"position":14,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"towards","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلنُّورِ ۚ","english":"the light","translit":"l-nūri","root":"نور"},{"position":16,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"And whoever","translit":"waman","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_011_017.mp3"},{"position":17,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنۢ","english":"believes","translit":"yu'min","root":"أمن","audio":"wbw/065_011_018.mp3"},{"position":18,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","english":"in Allah","translit":"bil-lahi","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_011_019.mp3"},{"position":19,"arabic":"وَيَعْمَلْ","english":"and does","translit":"wayaʿmal","root":"عمل","audio":"wbw/065_011_020.mp3"},{"position":20,"arabic":"صَـٰلِحًۭا","english":"righteous deeds","translit":"ṣāliḥan","root":"صلح","audio":"wbw/065_011_021.mp3"},{"position":21,"arabic":"يُدْخِلْهُ","english":"He will admit him","translit":"yud'khil'hu","root":"دخل","audio":"wbw/065_011_022.mp3"},{"position":22,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتٍۢ","english":"(into) Gardens","translit":"jannātin","root":"جنن","audio":"wbw/065_011_023.mp3"},{"position":23,"arabic":"تَجْرِى","english":"flow","translit":"tajrī","root":"جري","audio":"wbw/065_011_024.mp3"},{"position":24,"arabic":"مِن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_011_025.mp3"},{"position":25,"arabic":"تَحْتِهَا","english":"underneath it","translit":"taḥtihā","root":"تحت","audio":"wbw/065_011_026.mp3"},{"position":26,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ","english":"the rivers","translit":"l-anhāru","root":"نهر","audio":"wbw/065_011_027.mp3"},{"position":27,"arabic":"خَـٰلِدِينَ","english":"abiding","translit":"khālidīna","root":"خلد","audio":"wbw/065_011_028.mp3"},{"position":28,"arabic":"فِيهَآ","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_011_029.mp3"},{"position":29,"arabic":"أَبَدًۭا ۖ","english":"forever","translit":"abadan","root":"أبد","audio":"wbw/065_011_030.mp3"},{"position":30,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"Indeed","translit":"qad","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_011_032.mp3"},{"position":31,"arabic":"أَحْسَنَ","english":"Has been (granted) good","translit":"aḥsana","root":"حسن","audio":"wbw/065_011_033.mp3"},{"position":32,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"(by) Allah","translit":"l-lahu","root":"أله","audio":"wbw/065_011_034.mp3"},{"position":33,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","english":"for him","translit":"lahu","root":"","audio":"wbw/065_011_035.mp3"},{"position":34,"arabic":"رِزْقًا","english":"provision","translit":"riz'qan","root":"رزق","audio":"wbw/065_011_036.mp3"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"It is Allah who has created seven heavens and of the earth, the like of them. [His] command descends among them so you may know that Allah is over all things competent and that Allah has encompassed all things in knowledge.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","english":"Allah","translit":"al-lahu","root":"أله"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","english":"(is) He Who","translit":"alladhī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","english":"created","translit":"khalaqa","root":"خلق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَبْعَ","english":"seven","translit":"sabʿa","root":"سبع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"سَمَـٰوَٰتٍۢ","english":"heavens","translit":"samāwātin","root":"سمو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَمِنَ","english":"and of","translit":"wamina","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍi","root":"أرض"},{"position":8,"arabic":"مِثْلَهُنَّ","english":"(the) like of them","translit":"mith'lahunna","root":"مثل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"يَتَنَزَّلُ","english":"Descends","translit":"yatanazzalu","root":"نزل"},{"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْأَمْرُ","english":"the command","translit":"l-amru","root":"أمر"},{"position":11,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُنَّ","english":"between them","translit":"baynahunna","root":"بين"},{"position":12,"arabic":"لِتَعْلَمُوٓا۟","english":"that you may know","translit":"litaʿlamū","root":"علم"},{"position":13,"arabic":"أَنَّ","english":"that","translit":"anna","root":""},{"position":14,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":15,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"(is) on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":16,"arabic":"كُلِّ","english":"every","translit":"kulli","root":"كلل"},{"position":17,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","english":"thing","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":18,"arabic":"قَدِيرٌۭ","english":"All-Powerful","translit":"qadīrun","root":"قدر"},{"position":19,"arabic":"وَأَنَّ","english":"And that","translit":"wa-anna","root":""},{"position":20,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","english":"Allah","translit":"l-laha","root":"أله"},{"position":21,"arabic":"قَدْ","english":"indeed","translit":"qad","root":""},{"position":22,"arabic":"أَحَاطَ","english":"encompasses","translit":"aḥāṭa","root":"حوط"},{"position":23,"arabic":"بِكُلِّ","english":"all","translit":"bikulli","root":"كلل"},{"position":24,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","english":"things","translit":"shayin","root":"شيأ"},{"position":25,"arabic":"عِلْمًۢا","english":"(in) knowledge","translit":"ʿil'man","root":"علم"}]}]}
